{
  "texts": [
    "Interactive world models: Paralleling the interest in video generation models, interactive world models (Ha and Schmidhuber, 2018) have gained significant attention.",
    "Despite extensive research in this area, investigations have predominantly concentrated on video game environments Valevski et al. (2024); Che et al.",
    "(2024); Bruce et al. (2024).",
    "While a few contemporary studies have begun exploring real-world applications (e.g., Bar et al. (2024); Agarwal et al.",
    "(2025)), none explores interactions besides camera control or text."
  ]
}